### Local OpenAPI
GET http://127.0.0.1:3333/openapi.json
Accept: application/json

### Public Manifest (if tunnel)
GET {{PUBLIC_BASE_URL}}/chatgpt_tool_manifest.json
Accept: application/json

### MCP GET without SSE (expect 406 unless fallback enabled)
GET http://127.0.0.1:3333/mcp
Accept: application/json

### MCP GET with SSE
GET http://127.0.0.1:3333/mcp
Accept: text/event-stream

### MCP POST streaming (basic init message)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3333/mcp
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

